# Network Packet Sniffer

A beginner-friendly cybersecurity project built using Python and Scapy to capture and analyze network traffic in real time.

## Overview

This project demonstrates how packet sniffing works by capturing packets traversing a network interface and displaying useful information such as:

- Source IP Address
- Destination IP Address
- Protocol Type
- Packet Size

The project was created to learn networking fundamentals and packet analysis concepts used in cybersecurity.

## Features

- Live packet capture
- IP packet analysis
- TCP detection
- UDP detection
- ICMP detection
- Real-time monitoring
- Lightweight and easy to understand

## Technologies Used

- Python 3
- Scapy

